blue text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-8 inline-block hover:text-white transition-colors\",\"children\":\"вҶҗ Back to Case Studies\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-electric-blue/10 text-electric-blue border border-electric-blue/20 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\",\"children\":\"HealthTech\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-electric-blue/10 text-electric-blue border border-electric-blue/20 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\",\"children\":\"SaaS\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-electric-blue/10 text-electric-blue border border-electric-blue/20 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\",\"children\":\"AI Application\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight\",\"children\":\"AI Wellness Coach Web App\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl text-grey leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"Solen is a full-featured AI wellness coach providing conversational, empathetic guidance 24/7. Engineered as a complete \\\"business in a box\\\" with user authentication, subscription management, a bespoke admin dashboard, and an integrated blog CMS.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-12 pt-12 border-t border-white/10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-grey text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\",\"children\":\"Client\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white font-medium\",\"children\":\"Solen\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-grey text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\",\"children\":\"Product\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white font-medium\",\"children\":\"Solen Platform\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"col-span-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-grey text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\",\"children\":\"Deliverables\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white font-medium\",\"children\":\"Full-Stack Web App, AI Wellness Coach, Custom CMS\"}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"glass p-8 md:p-12 rounded-xl mb-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-display text-white mb-4\",\"children\":\"The Problem\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-grey leading-relaxed mb-6\",\"children\":\"The wellness app market is saturated with generic mood trackers and static content. Users need dynamic responses tailored to their emotional state. Moreover, running a SaaS typically requires complex DevOps, containerisation, and high server costs just to get off the ground.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-3 text-grey\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-start\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-electric-blue mr-3\",\"children\":\"вң—\"}],\" Generic, cookie-cutter advice instead of dynamic, contextual responses.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-start\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-electric-blue mr-3\",\"children\":\"вң—\"}],\" Complex onboarding deterring users seeking immediate help.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-start\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-electric-blue mr-3\",\"children\":\"вң—\"}],\" High operational overhead stitching together multiple expensive SaaS tools.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-start\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-electric-blue mr-3\",\"children\":\"вң—\"}],\" JavaScript-heavy stacks requiring complex DevOps and high server costs.\"]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-16\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-3xl font-display text-white mb-8 border-l-4 border-electric-blue pl-4\",\"children\":\"Our Approach\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-grey leading-relaxed mb-6\",\"children\":\"We designed Solen with a philosophy of maximum impact with minimum architectural friction. Rather than adopting a complex microservices architecture, we opted for a highly optimised monolithic approach to keep running costs incredibly low while delivering a highly interactive, React-powered frontend.\"}],\"$L3\"]}],\"$L4\",\"$L5\",\"$L6\",\"$L7\"]}]]}],null,\"$L8\"]}],\"isPartial\":false,\"staleTime\":300,\"varyParams\":null,\"buildId\":\"i9Cf0qMmt9f6Hl-9FDnLU\"}\n3:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-midnight p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/5\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white font-medium mb-2\",\"children\":\"Zero-Config DB\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-grey\",\"children\":\"SQLite3 auto-creates on first visit, making deployment as simple as FTP.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-midnight p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/5\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white font-medium mb-2\",\"children\":\"Edge Inference\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-grey\",\"children\":\"Cloudflare AI integration for highly empathetic, edge-optimised AI coaching.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-midnight p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/5\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white font-medium mb-2\",\"children\":\"Unified SaaS\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-grey\",\"children\":\"Marketing site, web app, blog, and admin tools all run from one codebase.\"}]]}]]}]\n4:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-3xl font-display text-white mb-8 border-l-4 border-electric-blue pl-4\",\"children\":\"What We Built\"}]\n5:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-12 mb-16\",\"children